data.description: Marvelous 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home situated in the desirable Keystone of Galvez subdivision. The Dayton II A floorplan features an open floorplan with laminate floors in the living room, granite countertops, and black appliances with 3CM full slab granite countertops, beautiful Birch cabinets, tankless hot water heater, and many more features that make this home energy efficient. Call to schedule your tour today!
